SELECT dbo.[User].[id], dbo.[User].[enabled], dbo.[User].[email], dbo.[Centrex_affectation_numero].[numero], dbo.[User].[Est_admin_centrex] FROM dbo.[User]
        LEFT JOIN dbo.[Centrex_affectation_numero]
        ON dbo.[User].[id] = dbo.[Centrex_affectation_numero].[id_user]
        WHERE dbo.[User].[email]
        IN ('ajoulin@bibas-murcia.fr','sebastien.lebourg@linkt.fr','quentin.dierre@linkt.fr','john.xerri@linkt.fr','sebastien.lebourg@linkt.fr')
        OR dbo.[Centrex_affectation_numero].[numero]
        IN ('0279370322')
